{"tid":681073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[死神來了]蘋果零售店結業？52 名員工受影響！","createTime":"2018-05-27T17:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T05:48:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc239c443a1bcaad3a5e9d1dd23a9d1ca15341a","tid":681073,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司近年不斷開設零售店，但面對目前科技產品普及下，用戶<span style=\"color: red;\">購買慾望減少，增長放緩</span>，似乎蘋果亦需要作出改變，近日有消息顯示，蘋果在美國地區，關閉一家零售店，影響 52 名員工。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，蘋果將關閉位於新澤西州大西洋城的一家零售店。蘋果向新澤西州提交了一份員工調整和再培訓通知，宣佈52人將因為這次結業店受到影響。蘋果在過去<span style=\"color: red;\">很少在不搬遷的情況下關閉一家零售店。</span><br />\n<br />\n蘋果表示，因為該區的旅遊人數大跌，不能再長期租下店舖，所以下了這個艱難的決定，將會為該店的員工，安排其他蘋果公司的工作崗位。<br />\n​<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/AppleRetailStore.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F03%2FAppleRetailStore.jpg&h=8c8c88c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/27/us-apple-retail-store-close/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2Fus-apple-retail-store-close%2F&d=Zcr1ZrsZHQSr%2BmlG7wDQarIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=079563fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/05/27/us-apple-retail-store-close/</a>"},{"pid":"9fa6ab0fbe0035cdd69a3248e8f1c87e4c363ec9","tid":681073,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T17:10:34.000Z","msg":"apple die<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895ac22098b271f89d3537706ef7231d9ceeba16","tid":681073,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"玩完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73da40b70b6cee71bd7ad6cf408c4ecc14d9cf94","tid":681073,"uid":16567,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27